        {
            "title": "大幅收緊限制 歐盟考慮以海事服務禁令取代俄羅斯石油價格上限機制",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Bloomberg calculations based on Finance Ministry's data\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"551\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/NOSZ2VKpBMLryFs4mxRzYQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU1MQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/2657aae5fa51fd64c8a1bd9e2c49fe0e\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Bloomberg calculations based on Finance Ministry's data</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 歐盟正在考慮一項提案，擬以禁止海事服務取代對<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:俄羅斯;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/俄羅斯\">俄羅斯</a>石油設定的價格上限，作為針對俄羅斯最新制裁方案的一部分。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">知情人士透露，若該舉措獲得成員國支持，歐洲企業將被禁止為俄羅斯石油運輸提供保險和運輸等必要服務，而不再以價格作為區分條件。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這些要求匿名的知情人士表示，全面禁令將大幅收緊對俄羅斯石油的限制，並使制裁執行更易實施。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">負責歐盟制裁事務的歐盟委員會發言人拒絕置評。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"551\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/b_bE3ssG7Y8aJw__1mx3VA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU1MQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/90f60e322f620c1eac520d5ad1326281\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">俄羅斯原油價格上限目前將自2月1日起降至每桶44.10美元。該定價機制每六個月進行一次審議，其設計原則是使價格門檻比烏拉爾原油平均市場價格低15%。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-cc1b2c33-2f17-3729-87fe-f48c999c8cdb-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">歐盟成員國已收到最新制裁方案潛在內容的簡報，這是自2022年俄羅斯全面入侵烏克蘭以來歐盟推出的第20輪制裁。歐盟力求在下月底前批准該方案。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">知情人士透露，歐盟制裁需全體成員國支持方能通過，目前已有若干國家示意反對用服務禁令取代價格上限機制。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題EU Mulls Replacing Russian Oil Price Cap With Ban on Services</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Alaric Nightingale.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%A4%A7%E5%B9%85%E6%94%B6%E7%B7%8A%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6-%E6%AD%90%E7%9B%9F%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E4%BB%A5%E6%B5%B7%E4%BA%8B%E6%9C%8D%E5%8B%99%E7%A6%81%E4%BB%A4%E5%8F%96%E4%BB%A3%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E7%9F%B3%E6%B2%B9%E5%83%B9%E6%A0%BC%E4%B8%8A%E9%99%90%E6%A9%9F%E5%88%B6-170758900.html",
