        {
            "title": "聯儲會理事米蘭稱凱文·沃什會是具有說服力且受人尊敬的主席",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:聯儲會;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/聯儲會\">聯儲會</a>理事斯蒂芬·米蘭表示，他預計川普提名的新任聯儲會主席凱文·沃什將在領導聯儲會貨幣政策委員會方面展現出很強的說服力。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「他長期以來都很擅長用自己的論點說服別人，所以我認為他會因此受到大量尊重，」米蘭周五在接受CNBC採訪時表示。「我認為人們會覺得他很有說服力，因為歸根結底，我認為他的很多觀點都是正確的，比如降低利率。​​」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：塵埃落定 川普選擇改頭換面的另一個凱文執掌聯儲會</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Fed’s Miran Sees Warsh as Persuasive, Respected New Chair</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-981a728c-b35e-3a30-a1ef-68f5f64e769e-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%81%AF%E5%84%B2%E6%9C%83%E7%90%86%E4%BA%8B%E7%B1%B3%E8%98%AD%E7%A8%B1%E5%87%B1%E6%96%87-%E6%B2%83%E4%BB%80%E6%9C%83%E6%98%AF%E5%85%B7%E6%9C%89%E8%AA%AA%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%9B%E4%B8%94%E5%8F%97%E4%BA%BA%E5%B0%8A%E6%95%AC%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD-164919678.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-31 01:48:53",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
